2:[["$","$L7",null,{"headerBgImage":"/images/articles/cloud-computing-price.png"}],["$","article",null,{"className":"article-page news-article-page","style":{"padding":0},"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"article-wrapper","style":{"padding":"0 24px"},"children":["$","span",null,{"className":"blog-entry-category","children":"20 March 2026"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"article-wrapper","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"article-content","children":[["$","h1",null,{"children":"AI日报：全球算力告急涨价，腾讯AI投入翻倍"}],["$","div",null,{"dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"<h3>1. 全球算力告急引发\"涨价潮\"</h3>\n<p>AWS和腾讯云之后，阿里云与百度云于3月19日同日官宣涨价，最高涨幅达34%。这意味着云计算十年\"价格战\"正式终结。</p>\n<p><strong>影响分析：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>中小企业成本压力增加</li>\n<li>AI算力需求持续旺盛</li>\n<li>云计算厂商盈利能力有望改善</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>2. 腾讯2026财年AI投入翻倍</h3>\n<p>稳扎稳打的腾讯也要为AI花大钱了。2026财年，腾讯将减少股票回购，AI投入翻倍。</p>\n<p><strong>关键点：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>AI投入大幅增加</li>\n<li>股票回购力度减少</li>\n<li>市场期待微信Agent和姚顺雨两张底牌</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>3. 英伟达新AI功能遭全网抵制</h3>\n<p>老黄怒怼玩家\"根本不懂AI\"，英伟达新AI功能遭全网抵制，游戏圈炸锅了。</p>\n\n<h3>行业观察</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>算力紧缺</strong>：AI爆发式增长导致全球算力供不应求</li>\n<li><strong>投资加码</strong>：科技巨头纷纷加大AI投入</li>\n<li><strong>争议显现</strong>：AI新技术应用面临用户接受度挑战</li>\n</ul>"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"share-links","children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"Twitter","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-twitter"}]}],["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"LinkedIn","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-linkedin-in"}]}],["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"Facebook","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-facebook-f"}]}]]}]]}]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-light pt-4 pb-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","h3",null,{"style":{"marginBottom":"24px","fontSize":"18px","fontWeight":700},"children":"其他新闻"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"posts-grid","children":[["$","div","openclaw-3-0",{"className":"col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4 blog-item","children":["$","div",null,{"c